Troubleshooting Tips
Wazuh Manager Not Starting:

Check logs: sudo tail -f /var/ossec/logs/ossec.log
Verify configuration: sudo /var/ossec/bin/wazuh-control info
Check disk space: df -h
Rules Not Triggering:

Validate rule syntax: sudo /var/ossec/bin/wazuh-logtest
Check decoder output: Test with sample log
Verify log file permissions: ls -la ~/endpoint-lab/logs/
Restart manager after rule changes: sudo systemctl restart wazuh-manager
Dashboard Not Accessible:

Check firewall: sudo ufw status
Verify service: sudo systemctl status wazuh-dashboard
Check port binding: sudo netstat -tlnp | grep 5601
Python Script Errors:

Verify Python version: python3 --version (requires 3.6+)
Install missing modules: pip3 install <module_name>
Check file paths and permissions
Use print statements for debugging
